Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:39.48,GEM,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll make it all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:04.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:18.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.00,0:01:22.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,They melted away...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.00,0:01:26.00,GEM,,0,0,0,,Why do I have the feeling this is getting worse?
